mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.plugin

Class GeoWaveFeatureReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.plugin.GeoWaveFeatureReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, org.geotools.data.FeatureReader<org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeatureType,org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeature>

    public class GeoWaveFeatureReader
extends Object
implements org.geotools.data.FeatureReader<org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeatureType,org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeature>
    This class wraps a geotools data store as well as one for statistics (for example to display Heatmaps) into a GeoTools FeatureReader for simple feature data. It acts as a helper for GeoWave's GeoTools data store.
